---
title: "WorkflowRouter.onReport - CRE Routing (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_role: onReport(workflowId, payload) called by CRE forwarder
    q_check_role --> q_validate_workflow: caller has FORWARDER_ROLE
    q_check_role --> q_revert_role: unauthorized
    q_revert_role --> [*]: revert Unauthorized
    q_validate_workflow --> q_decode: workflowId is registered
    q_validate_workflow --> q_revert_workflow: unknown workflow
    q_revert_workflow --> [*]: revert UnknownWorkflow
    q_decode --> q_route: decode target contract and function from workflow config
    q_route --> q_check_auction_mgmt: determine workflow type
    q_check_auction_mgmt --> q_call_perform: workflowType == AUCTION_MANAGEMENT
    q_check_auction_mgmt --> q_check_price_mgmt: not auction management
    q_call_perform --> q_forward_done: forward to auction.performUpkeep(performData)
    q_check_price_mgmt --> q_call_transmit: workflowType == PRICE_MANAGEMENT
    q_check_price_mgmt --> q_check_bidder: not price management
    q_call_transmit --> q_forward_done: forward to auction.transmit(priceData)
    q_check_bidder --> q_call_solver_bid: workflowType == AUCTION_BIDDER
    q_check_bidder --> q_revert_unknown: unknown workflow type
    q_call_solver_bid --> q_forward_done: forward to auctionBidder.bid(bidData)
    q_revert_unknown --> [*]: revert UnsupportedWorkflow
    q_forward_done --> [*]: return result

    note right of q_route
        INV-001: WorkflowRouter validates workflow registration before routing
        INV-002: Each workflow type maps to exactly one target contract and function
        INV-003: FORWARDER_ROLE granted only to CRE forwarder (trusted)
        INV-004: Provides modularity - workflow validation decoupled from business logic
    end note
